<%#
  Admin-only: deployment-state card. Phase 2 — wires up after the v0.16
  devnet deploy + Carl's Solana::Vault refactor. Right now the cells are
  placeholders explaining what each field will show.

  PHASE 2 HOOK POINTS — when wiring live data, the controller should
  set @vault_state via Solana::Vault.cached_vault_state (already exists
  for v0.15.1, signature will stay the same after Carl's refactor) and
  populate:
    @vault_paused              # bool
    @accepted_currencies       # Array<AcceptedCurrency> filtered to active
    @op_rev_balances           # Hash<currency_idx => u64>
  Then replace the <dd> "—" placeholders below with the real values.
%>
<section class="card border-2 border-primary/30 p-6 sm:p-8 mb-6">
  <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:gap-4 mb-2">
    <h2 class="text-heading font-bold text-xl">Live deployment state</h2>
    <span class="text-[11px] font-mono text-primary uppercase tracking-wider">admin only</span>
  </div>
  <p class="text-warning text-sm mb-5 max-w-3xl">
    Phase 2 &mdash; wires up after v0.16 devnet deploy. Fields below are placeholders so the layout
    is ready when Carl's Rails refactor lands.
  </p>

  <dl class="grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">

    <div class="bg-surface-alt border border-subtle rounded-lg p-4">
      <dt class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary font-semibold mb-1">Program ID</dt>
      <dd class="font-mono text-xs sm:text-sm text-heading break-all">
        <%# Phase 2: read from Solana::Config::PROGRAM_ID at request time. %>
        <%= (Solana::Config::PROGRAM_ID rescue "Dx8uGU5w7B9NytDSsW4kseGZuqdVVRq1KY1mGXN2GaCT") %>
      </dd>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-muted mt-1">Same on devnet + mainnet builds &mdash; pinned via SOLANA_PROGRAM_ID.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-surface-alt border border-subtle rounded-lg p-4">
      <dt class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary font-semibold mb-1">Upgrade authority</dt>
      <dd class="font-mono text-xs sm:text-sm text-heading break-all">
        BW13kgfiG2koFn3WRkte21NW9TFygsD1ge2fNJdjH6kC
      </dd>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-muted mt-1">Squads V4 2-of-3 vault PDA. Only the Squad can ship upgrades.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-surface-alt border border-subtle rounded-lg p-4">
      <dt class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary font-semibold mb-1">Paused</dt>
      <dd class="font-mono text-sm text-muted">
        <%# Phase 2: replace with @vault_state&.paused ? "yes" : "no". %>
        &mdash; <span class="text-[11px] text-muted">live data, wires after deploy</span>
      </dd>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-muted mt-1">Read from VaultState.paused via the cached vault-state preload.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-surface-alt border border-subtle rounded-lg p-4">
      <dt class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary font-semibold mb-1">Registered currencies</dt>
      <dd class="font-mono text-sm text-muted">
        <%# Phase 2: iterate @accepted_currencies, render mint + active flag. %>
        &mdash; <span class="text-[11px] text-muted">live data, wires after deploy</span>
      </dd>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-muted mt-1">accepted_currencies[16], filtered to active = true.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-surface-alt border border-subtle rounded-lg p-4">
      <dt class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary font-semibold mb-1">Operator revenue (USDC)</dt>
      <dd class="font-mono text-sm text-muted">
        <%# Phase 2: @op_rev_balances[0] formatted as dollars. %>
        &mdash; <span class="text-[11px] text-muted">live data, wires after deploy</span>
      </dd>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-muted mt-1">Balance in the per-currency op_rev ATA. Sweepable to Squads vault.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-surface-alt border border-subtle rounded-lg p-4">
      <dt class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary font-semibold mb-1">Treasury authority</dt>
      <dd class="font-mono text-xs text-muted break-all">
        <%# Phase 2: pull from @vault_state&.treasury_authority once the field exists. %>
        &mdash; <span class="text-[11px] text-muted">pinned at initialize</span>
      </dd>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-muted mt-1">Destination owner for sweep_operator_revenue. Set once, immutable.</p>
    </div>

  </dl>
</section>
